channel.title: Cant get server online
channel.description: Ok Guys like 5 months ago on this laptop my server was up, i used a auto pf program. But now for some reason when i try runnning it everything seems fine but it says that its offline, help please guys. Btw i reacently tried getting it online via utorrent, but it still doesnt work ! help please guys.

item.title: Cant get server online
item.dc:creator: @rafikd rafikd
item.description:
@rafikd wrote:

[code]go to
www.canyouseeme.org

it will show you your ip, in the
“what port?” box type

43594

which is the default server port

now PRESS “CHECK” DON’T USE ENTER, OR IT WONT WORK! it fool’d me too in the start.
if it says:
Error: I could not see your service on ...* on port (43594)
Reason: Connection timed out[/code]
Your portforwarding is NOT successful

but if it says success then you have successfully portforwarded when you’ve checked post again and ill see what i can do
